t: "∆Āe he…ďaali feere resugol …ďen yo …ďe habbo haa Alla al…óinira …ďe ∆Āural Makko ngal. ∆Āen wonu…ďe …óa…ď…ďude soottaade e …ďen …ďe √Īaame moo…óon jeyi, soottaadede …ďe si on anndii e ma…ď…ďe mo∆ī∆īere, jonnee …ďe immorde e jawdi Alla ndin, ndin ndi O jonni on, wata on waawnu hor…ďe moo…óon …ďen e fii jeeno, si …ďe faandike saŇčaade, wata on …óa…ď…ďu jawkal ngurndam aduna, kala waawnuu…óo …ďe pellet, Alla …ďaawo baawnugol …ďe ko O Surroowo Yurmitee…óo"